{"fields":[{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasPrompt"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt0"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt1"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt3"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt4"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt5"},{"t":"B","v":"false","n":"HasRevealPrompt6"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke0"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke1"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke2"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke3"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke4"},{"t":"B","v":"true","n":"HasRevealJoke5"},{"t":"A","s":"Was ist dein erster Gedanke an einem Montagmorgen?","n":"RevealPrompt0"},{"t":"A","s":"Wer feiert am Freitag eher um 18.00 Uhr?","n":"RevealPrompt1"},{"t":"A","s":"Du hast 24 Stunden ganz für dich allein, was wirst du damit machen?","n":"RevealPrompt3"},{"t":"A","s":"Was macht den Mittwoch besonders?","n":"RevealPrompt4"},{"t":"A","s":"Warum ist der Donnerstag eigentlich besser als der Freitag?","n":"RevealPrompt5"},{"t":"A","s":"Wer hat keine Schwierigkeiten, am Sonntag bis mittags zu schlafen?","n":"RevealPrompt6"},{"t":"A","s":"8 Stunden nichts geschafft. Jetzt endlich Feierabend! Juhu!","v":"joke1","n":"RevealJoke0"},{"t":"A","s":"Manchmal muss man sich auch etwas Schlaf gönnen.","v":"joke6","n":"RevealJoke1"},{"t":"A","s":"Ich hasse Montage...","v":"joke0","n":"RevealJoke2"},{"t":"A","s":"Klingt auf jeden Fall sehr entspannend.","v":"joke3","n":"RevealJoke3"},{"t":"A","s":"Es ist Mittwoch, meine Kerle!","v":"joke4","n":"RevealJoke4"},{"t":"A","s":"Freunde, Donnerstag ist bekanntlich Dönerstag!","v":"joke5","n":"RevealJoke5"},{"t":"A","s":"Welcher Wochentag repräsentiert euch am besten?","v":"prompt","n":"Prompt"}]}